INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 2.16.0 (2021-05-02)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.9
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.8

* Version 2.15.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.14.1 (2020-11-29)
B: Adjust return code for monit service check

* Version 2.14.0 (2020-11-28)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (openssh_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 2.13.4 (2020-11-19)
E: Ensure lineinfile tasks can create file if missing

* Version 2.13.3 (2020-11-09)
B: Activate moduli disable task for OpenBSD

* Version 2.13.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 2.13.1 (2020-10-20)
E: Add missing header to moduli file

* Version 2.13.0 (2020-10-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 2.12.0 (2020-05-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 2.11.1 (2020-02-24)
E: Use Ansible module copy instead of template for static moduli file

* Version 2.11.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 2.10.0 (2019-10-18)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.6
